      <textAnnotation id="sid-A4038C71-4157-47BE-A259-77B14C3D5ED8" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Financial Posting will be replicated realtime from individual S4 box to CFIN system
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-4758C15A-AC54-4470-9CC7-4F8FB9AC65B3" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>For Non-Control Countries: Company Codes which have inhouse bank relationship
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <group categoryValueRef="sid-981ec24e-b756-4951-8975-bc370d6c8943" id="sid-DDA9CB34-20D2-4669-915B-AB949F87DBCF">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel align="center" ref="text_name" valign="middle" x="23.0" y="-17.0"/>
         </extensionElements>
      </group>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-A0421866-7B48-49ED-B984-69EE047B0429" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Cashless settlement – Settlement of Invoices via F110 run without actual movement of funds. This involves use of an In-House Bank center which nets all payments and receipts between IHB participants and converts them to Intercompany loans on which interest is charged/paid.
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
   </process>
